window.bookSummaryJSON = "When her best friend and neighbor, Margaret, comes to her with a problem, Clementine goes to many lengths to help her friend. This sets off a rollicking adventure-filled week that finds Clementine getting into and out of further trouble, while learning valuable life lessons. <p>In <i>Clementine</i>, Sara Pennypacker has created a precocious red-headed third-grader who will be instantly loved by young audiences.</p>"; 
